nodes.text: Lando's cane was a cane that belonged to the human smuggler Landonis Balthazar Calrissian, who used it during the First Order/Resistance War. Its head was sculpted to resemble Calrissian's beloved Cloud City and featured the inscription "Baron Landonis Calrissian."
Lando's cane first appeared in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, the third and final installment of the Star Wars sequel trilogy.
